snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' : Spider-Man Version 2 [Teaser Trailer] [FNF MOD]
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' Spider-Man Mod Version 2 Trailer. No demo will be released. Enjoy

Face off new villians with Spider-man by your side!
We promise a remastered version of the original mod, 3 new villians, bonus songs, new sets of covers, and hard effort

Featuring :
'@Driftyboyy0' as Spiderman [Lead Director/ Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/driftyboyy0

'@T8KU_' (Taco) as Mysterio [Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/T8KU_

'@fyukoberry' as Girlfriend [Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/fyukoberry

'@BigWesG_VO' as Green Goblin [Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/BigWesG_VO

'@screamingneko' (Shekkai47) as Venom and Doc Ock [Music / Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/mothershekkai

'@notXxXayne' as Electro [Voice Actor] : https://twitter.com/notxxxayne?s=21&t=XRv3tq2K8oBF5iltWZo-jg

'@Liltico_' (Lil Tico) [Music] : https://twitter.com/Liltico_

'@SpringVeryEpic' (SpringIsEpic) [Primary Charter] : https://twitter.com/SpringVeryEpic

'@MagicansWRLD' [Secondary Charter] : https://twitter.com/MagiciansWRLD

'@SKG_Art' [Animator / Version 2 Programmer] : https://twitter.com/SKG_Art

'RealKyofu' [Version 1 Programmer] : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUTqIUFwC6TVP_95jo4JQRw

'@Creezo_tweets' [Version 1 Backgrounds] : https://twitter.com/Creezo_tweets

'@JazzyLadd' [Version 2 Backgrounds] :https://twitter.com/3_cinnamonroll

Engine : FNF Psych Engine, created by '@ShadowMario' : https://twitter.com/Shadow_Mario_

Other Needed Credits Are Located on the Page / In-game

If you're looking to play, here is the link. Please enjoy!
There will be no demo for version 2 if you're trying to look for it

Gamebanana : https://gamebanana.com/mods/348649

All Rights Goes to Disney Inc, Marvel Entertainment Clip & Photo Licensing | Marvel Studios
I also think Sony owns it but yea
Please don't sue us, we have no cash and we ain't even profiting off this.
again, WE ARE NOT MAKING MONEY OFF OF THIS.

Trailer Song : Farewell - Lena Raine (Apart of Celeste)

#FridayNightFunkin #Spiderman #SpringIsEpic
